üîÑ Shared Behaviors
Component	Requirement
Authentication	Multi-guard (providers & staff) via Laravel Breeze
2FA	Email or phone using pragmarx/google2fa-laravel
Caching	Redis for profile caching, access tracking, and analytics
Notifications	Laravel Mailables + SMS channel integration
Analytics Worker	Scheduled Artisan command to compute provider ranking
File Storage	Laravel Storage facade (public disk)
Error Handling	Inertia shared prop for global error flash
Rate Limiting	Throttle login, password reset, booking submission
